{"search_data": "ChhattisgarhCG Mukhyamantri Vishwakarma Nirman Shramik Mrityu Evam Divyang Sahayata Yojana 2020CG govt. Mukhyamantri Vishwakarma Nirman Shramik Mrityu Evam Divyang Sahayata Yojana for registered construction labourers & CM Asangathit Karmkaar Mrityu Evam Divyang Sahayata Yojana 2020 for unorganized sector workers, Rs. 50,000 in case of disability & Rs. 1 lakh in case of death at workCG Mukhyamantri Vishwakarma Nirman Shramik Mrityu Evam Divyang Sahayata Yojana 2020The important features and highlights of this scheme are as follows:-Chhattisgarh building and Other Construction Workers Welfare Board of Labour Department will implement CG Mukhyamantri Vishwakarma Nirman Shramik Mrityu Evam Divyang Sahayata Yojana.This scheme is for all registered construction labourers in the age group of 18 to 60 years.All of them will get Rs. 50,000 if they get disabled during work.The state govt. will provide Rs. 1 lakh to families of construction Labourers in case they die at work.However, if the death of nirmaan shramik occurs due to substance abuse or suicide, then labourers would not be entitled for any benefit.CG Mukhyamantri Asangathit Karmkaar Mrityu Evam Divyang Sahayata Yojana 2020Chhattisgarh Unorganised Labourer Social Security Board of Labour Department will implement CG Mukhyamantri Asangathit Karmkaar Mrityu Evam Divyang Sahayata Yojana.This scheme is for all registered unorganized sector labourers in the age group of 18 to 60 years. All of them will get Rs. 50,000 if they get disabled during work while Rs. 1 lakh would be given to their family in case they die at work. It is important to note that both these scheme benefits are not applicable in case the death of labourer occurs due to substance abuse or suicide.  Sarkari Yojana App - Download Now Source / Reference Link: https://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/city/raipur/chhattisgarh-ahead-of-rural-polls-cm-sop-for-labourers-of-unorganised-sector/articleshow/73065287.cms  at  "}